{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"gamepadconnected","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>gamepadconnected</code> 事件会在浏览器检测到游戏控制器第一次连接或者第一次按下游戏键/摇杆的时候触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本信息","title":"基本信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"文档\">文档</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/gamepad/#the-gamepadconnected-event\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad</a></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"类型\">类型</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>事件</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"冒泡\">冒泡</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>No</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"可取消\">可取消</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>No</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>DefaultView (<code>&lt;window&gt;</code>)</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"默认操着\">默认操着</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>无</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Property</th>\n      <th>Type</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>target</code> 只读</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件目标（DOM 树中的顶层，即 document.documentElement）。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>type</code> 只读</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件的类型。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>bubbles</code> 只读</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件是否正常冒泡。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>cancelable</code> 只读</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件是否可以取消。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr